# Phase 62 Wave 0 — multi-DB isolation pinned without the LRU.
#
# Wave 0 stages this fixture as a no-op via `halt`. Plan 04 (Wave 3) pins
# the post-LRU-removal contract: ATTACH 17+ databases sequentially in a
# single session and verify CREATE on each succeeds, with DESCRIBE on the
# FIRST one still working (pre-Phase-62 the LRU would have evicted DB #1
# on the 17th ATTACH and surfaced a "catalog context evicted" error).
#
# Behavioural property pinned (from RESEARCH.md §6):
#   B15: multi-DB isolation preserved without LRU (sqllogictest companion
#        to test_multi_db_isolation.py)

require semantic_views

statement ok
LOAD semantic_views;

halt

# Phase 62 Plan 04: ATTACH 17+ databases sequentially in a single
# session; CREATE SEMANTIC VIEW v_N on each; DESCRIBE on the FIRST one
# must succeed (pre-Phase-62 the LRU would have evicted it on the 17th
